a, b, c, d, N
f(x,y) = a * x + b * y
c * x + d * y \leq N
x \geq 0, y \geq 0
N
lcm(c, d)
F(x,y,\lambda,\lambda_1,\lambda_2) = ax + by + \lambda(x) + \lambda_1(y) - \lambda_2(cx + dy - N)
F_x = a + \lambda - \lambda_2c = 0
F_y = b + \lambda_1 - \lambda_2d = 0
\lambda(x) + \lambda(y)
